<div class="section_title">Award categories</div>
<span class="text">
Best of CES distinction is awarded to one product from each of the following 10 categories: 
<UL>
<LI><B>Accessories:</B> Peripheral devices and software that enhance the other categories without replacing them. Includes innovative apparel, adapters, carrying cases, and add-ons. </LI>
<LI><B>Auto, Marine, and RV:</B> Anything that goes in your car, boat, or RV. Includes car stereo systems, car alarms, mobile entertainment systems, satellite antennas, fixed navigation systems, and other in-dash systems. </LI>
<LI><B>High-End Audio:</B> For the real audiophile. Includes tube amps, high-end speaker systems, external digital-to-analog decoders, and ultrahigh-quality media players. </LI>
<LI><B>High-End Video:</B> High-definition TVs and display technologies including rear-projection TVs, projectors, DLPs, LCOS displays, and high-end video components. </LI>
<LI><B>Home Audio and Video:</B> Consumer-level amps, all-in-one home theater systems, PVRs, 5.1 audio systems, speakers, and components. </LI>
<LI><B>Home Media Devices:</B> Media servers and receivers. Includes devices that manage, distribute, and aggregate all your home digital media. </LI>
<LI><B>Home Networking and Automation:</B> Everything for wiring your home. Includes wireless and Ethernet networking gateways, routers, and peripherals. Kits to automate your home appliances, lights, and security. Also includes hardware and software to control such conveniences as wireless sprinkler systems, automated speech controls, and remote access. </LI>
<LI><B>Mobile Computing and Wireless:</B> Portable systems and mobile wireless devices. Includes PDAs, handheld GPS devices, handheld computers, wireless add-ons, cellular phones, 2.5 and 3G handsets, and other portable data devices. </LI>
<LI><B>Photo and Imaging:</B> Anything that helps you take or print better pictures. Includes digital cameras, photo printers, scanners, photo-finishing devices and services, ink, and paper. </LI>
<LI><B>Portable Audio and Video:</B> Includes portable digital audio and video players, DV and analog camcorders, portable DVD players, and portable displays. </LI></UL><BR><SPAN class=subhead>Best of the Best</SPAN> 
<UL>
<LI><B>Best of Show:</B> One overall Best of Show award is given out to the best product at CES, as voted by the judges. The winner from each category is eligible for this award.</LI></UL>
</span>
